comments: Fox (SAC) cleanly dislodges the ball from Giddey (OKC) at the end of his drive, and is last to make contact as the ball goes out of bounds.
Huerter (SAC) legally contests Giddey's (OKC) jump shot attempt.
Murray (SAC) establishes himself in Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) reaches in and marginal contact occurs with Fox's (SAC) arm as he makes the pass.
Giddey (OKC) cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt by Fox (SAC).

Giddey (OKC) is the last player to make contact with the ball before it goes out of bounds. After communicating with the Replay Center, it is determined that Huerter's (SAC) shot attempt made contact with the rim and the shot clock is reset to 14 when play resumes.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) reaches in and marginal contact occurs with Fox (SAC) during his drive.
Williams (OKC) initiates contact with Fox's (SAC) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) hooks Barnes' (SAC) left arm, affecting his SQBR before he makes contact with the ball.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes three steps to the basket.
Williams (OKC) commits a take foul on Murray (SAC).
Joe (OKC) initiates body contact to Huerter (SAC) as he receives the pass that causes him to step OOB.
Huerter (SAC) steps out of bounds while still in possession of the ball.
